The Peoples Democratic Party’s governorship candidate in the just concluded Osun election, Ademola Adeleke, has been granted bail. He was granted bail at the Mpape Magistrate Court. Confirming the development is a video of Adeleke after the judgement in court on its official Twitter handle, PDP wrote: “Adeleke, the PDP Governor-Elect of Osun State who was earlier arraigned before an Mpape magistrate court has been granted bail. “ Sen. Adeleke was granted bail in the sum of N2 M and a surety in like sum. “The matter has been adjourned to 24th of June 2019.” 